    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《法术工匠》是一款回合制策略类Roguelike游戏，您可以利用智慧融合法术创造新组合。您可以单人游戏或和朋友在线合作！</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>发现聪明组合</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>法术系统深邃且强大</strong>：法术可以互相影响，创造无数的创新可能。例如，当您对敌人施放“Swap”时，接下来组合中的法术将攻击您传送离开的原始位置，您可以因此将附近的敌人链接在一起，然后跟随一个强力的伤害法术，一次性击败所有敌人！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>《法术工匠》奖励变化和创造力</strong>：法术使用得越多，消耗成本就会越高，随着回合的推进，成本会降低，因此我们鼓励您经常尝试新策略。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1618380/extras/6ed201f014177236d33a81e4337ee8f3.poster.avif?t=1768337996\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1618380/extras/6ed201f014177236d33a81e4337ee8f3.webm?t=1768337996\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1618380/extras/6ed201f014177236d33a81e4337ee8f3.mp4?t=1768337996\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>炸飞你的朋友们！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与您的朋友在<strong>在线合作模式</strong>中共同冒险。彼此拯救于死亡边缘，或者意外炸飞对方！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《法术工匠》采用独特的<strong>“阵营制”回合系统</strong>，您和您的朋友可以同时行动，保持动作不停歇。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1618380/extras/178024ba14002986709d85021f148657.poster.avif?t=1768337996\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1618380/extras/178024ba14002986709d85021f148657.webm?t=1768337996\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1618380/extras/178024ba14002986709d85021f148657.mp4?t=1768337996\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>专注于您的魔法</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >符文系统为您的魔法潜力增加了一个全新的层次，通过增强和专精您的魔法。如果您想成为一个携带诅咒四处感染敌人的瘟疫法师，您完全可以做到。或者成为一个在每次传送时创造自己复制体的死灵法师，并且有随机机会复活他所击杀的敌人为己所用？没错，可能性无穷无尽。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1618380/extras/388ecbdb7b83c5436b68b8c8fe4049d4.poster.avif?t=1768337996\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1618380/extras/388ecbdb7b83c5436b68b8c8fe4049d4.webm?t=1768337996\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1618380/extras/388ecbdb7b83c5436b68b8c8fe4049d4.mp4?t=1768337996\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>挑战与回报</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >冠军级敌人提供了额外的特殊挑战。它们具有增长型或具备复制自身的“Slime”等修饰词，使得您需要赶快击败它们。冠军敌人将迫使您超越最喜欢的策略，想出新的方法。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1618380/extras/b516835ba8cd75ec538bb4c6f773625b.poster.avif?t=1768337996\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1618380/extras/b516835ba8cd75ec538bb4c6f773625b.webm?t=1768337996\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1618380/extras/b516835ba8cd75ec538bb4c6f773625b.mp4?t=1768337996\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>揭开秘密和突破</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >找到聪明的方式<strong>突破最大法力限制</strong>，施放极其强大的法术。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一些法术以强大且意想不到的方式结合，社区的玩家们总是不断发现新秘密。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1618380/extras/cd9b2b368620d8aea78f653631e78644.poster.avif?t=1768337996\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1618380/extras/cd9b2b368620d8aea78f653631e78644.webm?t=1768337996\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1618380/extras/cd9b2b368620d8aea78f653631e78644.mp4?t=1768337996\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>我会喜欢《法术工匠》吗？</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《法术工匠》是一款精心设计、富有挑战性且引人深思的回合制游戏。慢慢来，发挥创造力，目睹您的计划完美展开，就像您那小小的邪恶心愿一样！</p>",
